author: Shelli Weinstein, TV GUIDE
title: Find Out When Pretty Little Liars, The Fosters and More ABC Family Shows Return
text:
ABC Family, which will be going by the name of Freeform in January, has announced more of its winter lineup.
We knew that Pretty Little Liars ' sixth season will kick off on Tuesday, Jan. 12 at 8/7c, followed by the series premiere of the Mortal Instruments fantasy series Shadowhunters , and now we know when we can catch up with The Fosters , Young & Hungry and more.
The Fosters will return for its third season on Monday, Jan. 18 at 8/7c along with the new series Recovery Road , based on the YA novel of the same name, following a teenage girl facing the struggle of addiction.
This Shadowhunters first look of Clary meeting Jace is everything
Sitcoms Young & Hungry and Baby Daddy will premiere on Wednesday, Feb. 3 at 8/7c and 8:30/7:30c, respectively.
Which premiere are you most excited for?
